<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Quod vero Alexandriam propter immensam et repentinam famem inconsulto se adisset, questus est</SPAN> (<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Tiberius</SPAN>) <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">in senatu</SPAN>


