<SPAN CLASS="whole">Ra‑messu</SPAN> II (1333 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>); the <SPAN CLASS="whole">semi-mythical</SPAN> Sesostris (Sesosis) of Herodotus and Diodorus: the list of his conquests is, of course, mainly fabulous.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
